videos.headline: Longhorn dives for six
videos.description: Texas QB Tyrone Swoopes tosses the ball downfield to TE Caleb Bluiett, who runs and dives across the goal line to score a 57-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Baylor's McGowan gets first career carry
videos.description: 6-foot-7, 410-pound Baylor TE LaQuan McGowan lines up in the backfield for his first career rushing attempt.

videos.headline: C. Johnson run for 4 yds,C. Johnson fumbled, forced by P. Locke III, recovered by Texas A. Wheeler
videos.description: Chris Johnson run for 4 yards to the Bayl 18 Chris Johnson fumbled, forced by P.J. Locke III, recovered by Texas Anthony Wheeler

videos.headline: L. Hawthorne run for 17 yds for a 1ST down
videos.description: Lynx Hawthorne run for 17 yds to the Texas 42 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Benches clear between Texas and Baylor
videos.description: After Baylor's Lynx Hawthorne throws an interception to Texas' Duke Thomas, Hawthorne makes a late tackle, which causes players from the Bears' sideline to run across the field.

videos.headline: L. Hawthorne pass intercepted,J. Hall return  for 17 yds,TEXAS penalty, Offensive Holding (P. Locke III)
videos.description: Lynx Hawthorne pass intercepted Jason Hall return for 17 yds to the Bayl 46 TEXAS Penalty, Offensive Holding (P.J. Locke III) to the Bayl 42

videos.headline: J. Jefferson run for 20 yds for a TD
videos.description: Johnny Jefferson run for 20 yds for a TD

videos.headline: The Lynx is loose
videos.description: Baylor's fourth-string QB Lynx Hawthorne scrambles to the right and dives for the near-side pylon to score an 8-yard touchdown against Texas.

videos.headline: Baylor fumbles after converting fourth down
videos.description: On 4th-and-four, Baylor's Johnny Jefferson runs up the middle for a 12-yard gain but coughs the ball up to Texas with just over two minutes remaining in the fourth quarter.
